know, and among men,

00:38:58.900 --> 00:39:02.290 align:middle line:84%
as the ethers seem to
be refining to the point

00:39:02.290 --> 00:39:04.670 align:middle line:84%
where everything can
begin bubbling closer

00:39:04.670 --> 00:39:07.320 align:middle line:84%
to the surface, tremendous
amounts of resentment

00:39:07.320 --> 00:39:08.840 align:middle line:90%
and anger--

00:39:08.840 --> 00:39:09.550 align:middle line:90%
>>HARVEY: Rage.

00:39:09.550 --> 00:39:11.050 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: --are
starting to surface.

00:39:11.050 --> 00:39:13.160 align:middle line:84%
Now let's look at that
part, because we can't just

00:39:13.160 --> 00:39:15.740 align:middle line:84%
go into love and light without
acknowledging the rage.

00:39:15.740 --> 00:39:17.155 align:middle line:90%
>>HARVEY: Oh, God, no.

00:39:17.155 --> 00:39:18.530 align:middle line:84%
I'm not a love
and light brigade.

00:39:18.530 --> 00:39:19.080 align:middle line:90%
You know me.

00:39:19.080 --> 00:39:20.788 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I know, so
let's talk about it.

00:39:20.788 --> 00:39:22.910 align:middle line:84%
Most people are looking
for love and light.

00:39:22.910 --> 00:39:25.460 align:middle line:84%
But this is sitting right
there, ready to come up.

00:39:25.460 --> 00:39:26.110 align:middle line:84%
>>HARVEY: We're
never going to find

00:39:26.110 --> 00:39:28.140 align:middle line:84%
the true love and the
true light without going

00:39:28.140 --> 00:39:29.760 align:middle line:90%
through the shadow.

00:39:29.760 --> 00:39:31.470 align:middle line:84%
But what we have
to evolve-- Let's

00:39:31.470 --> 00:39:33.550 align:middle line:84%
take the male female
problem, and let's

00:39:33.550 --> 00:39:36.950 align:middle line:84%
try and look at it from the
Jesus perspective together.

00:39:36.950 --> 00:39:40.790 align:middle line:84%
It's obvious that patriarchy
has wounded, and betrayed,

00:39:40.790 --> 00:39:44.310 align:middle line:84%
and humiliated, and degraded
women at the deepest level.

00:39:44.310 --> 00:39:47.120 align:middle line:84%
Made them into
whores, or Madonnas,

00:39:47.120 --> 00:39:50.470 align:middle line:84%
or purveyors of
original sin, and made

00:39:50.470 --> 00:39:53.030 align:middle line:84%
them deeply self-loathing
of the very things

00:39:53.030 --> 00:39:57.010 align:middle line:84%
that women should be
so gloriously proud of.

00:39:57.010 --> 00:39:59.470 align:middle line:84%
Their bodies, the
power of creation

00:39:59.470 --> 00:40:01.017 align:middle line:84%
that is given to
a woman, the fact

00:40:01.017 --> 00:40:03.580 align:middle line:84%
that a woman is really a
representative, an ambassador,

00:40:03.580 --> 00:40:07.890 align:middle line:84%
a living vision of
the divine mother.

00:40:07.890 --> 00:40:09.360 align:middle line:90%
My God.

00:40:09.360 --> 00:40:11.350 align:middle line:84%
And the same thing
is being done to men,

00:40:11.350 --> 00:40:14.740 align:middle line:84%
because you can't
make an oppressor

00:40:14.740 --> 00:40:18.490 align:middle line:84%
class without secretly
oppressing the heart,

00:40:18.490 --> 00:40:20.600 align:middle line:84%
and soul, and body
of the oppressor.

00:40:20.600 --> 00:40:23.270 align:middle line:84%
So men are cut off from
the feminine they degrade.

00:40:23.270 --> 00:40:28.050 align:middle line:84%
And women are annihilated by
pain, and resentment, and rage

00:40:28.050 --> 00:40:30.690 align:middle line:84%
at everything that
they've suffered.

00:40:30.690 --> 00:40:35.920 align:middle line:84%
What's necessary now, I
think, is for men and women

00:40:35.920 --> 00:40:40.210 align:middle line:84%
to evolve a way of being
with each other in which

00:40:40.210 --> 00:40:47.930 align:middle line:84%
these deep-seated, cellular
agonies can be talked about,

00:40:47.930 --> 00:40:51.580 align:middle line:84%
can be opened up,
while not accusing

00:40:51.580 --> 00:40:54.294 align:middle line:84%
the other person of being
the representative of it.

00:40:54.294 --> 00:40:54.960 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:40:54.960 --> 00:40:55.580 align:middle line:90%
Exactly.

00:40:55.580 --> 00:40:58.077 align:middle line:84%
>>AUDIENCE: So many men--
straight guys that I love

00:40:58.077 --> 00:41:00.035 align:middle line:84%
and who are my buddies--
come up to me and say,

00:41:00.035 --> 00:41:01.250 align:middle line:90%
you have no idea.

00:41:01.250 --> 00:41:01.750 align:middle line:90%
I can't.

00:41:01.750 --> 00:41:05.390 align:middle line:84%
I am not personally
responsible for the last 2,500

00:41:05.390 --> 00:41:06.600 align:middle line:90%
years of patriarchy.

00:41:06.600 --> 00:41:09.980 align:middle line:84%
I'm trying very hard
to be a metro-sexual.

00:41:09.980 --> 00:41:11.210 align:middle line:90%
I'm trying to be kind.

00:41:11.210 --> 00:41:13.160 align:middle line:90%
I'm trying to be sensitive.

00:41:13.160 --> 00:41:16.035 align:middle line:84%
I've read Clarissa Pinkola
Estes and Betty Friedan.

00:41:16.035 --> 00:41:17.410 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But
nothing is working.

00:41:17.410 --> 00:41:19.400 align:middle line:84%
>>HARVEY: Nothing
is working because I

00:41:19.400 --> 00:41:24.602 align:middle line:84%
am being held to account for
crimes I myself know are awful.

00:41:24.602 --> 00:41:27.330 align:middle line:84%
And I'm really
trying to transform.

00:41:27.330 --> 00:41:30.060 align:middle line:90%
And this is not working.

00:41:30.060 --> 00:41:31.060 align:middle line:90%
And the same with women.

00:41:31.060 --> 00:41:33.510 align:middle line:84%
I think that women
really need to be

00:41:33.510 --> 00:41:36.815 align:middle line:84%
able to voice their
outrage and their pain

00:41:36.815 --> 00:41:42.220 align:middle line:84%
without identifying with it,
because they are not just

00:41:42.220 --> 00:41:43.270 align:middle line:90%
their rage.

00:41:43.270 --> 00:41:45.760 align:middle line:90%
They are the divine mother.

00:41:45.760 --> 00:41:48.960 align:middle line:84%
And I think the
key is two things.

00:41:48.960 --> 00:41:53.080 align:middle line:84%
First, women to connect with
the divine motherhood of God.

00:41:53.080 --> 00:41:56.160 align:middle line:84%
And men to connect with
the divine masculine.

00:41:56.160 --> 00:41:59.860 align:middle line:84%
And to be empowered at
a sacred level by both.

00:41:59.860 --> 00:42:01.360 align:middle line:90%
Both need to be there.

00:42:01.360 --> 00:42:03.650 align:middle line:84%
And then, when
they come together,

00:42:03.650 --> 00:42:06.590 align:middle line:84%
to do practices, very
simple practices,

00:42:06.590 --> 00:42:10.820 align:middle line:84%
that can align the man and the
woman with their divine truth.

00:42:10.820 --> 00:42:15.560 align:middle line:84%
And then to speak like
you speak if you're

00:42:15.560 --> 00:42:17.935 align:middle line:84%
an Israeli or a Palestinian
in a hostage negotiation.

00:42:17.935 --> 00:42:20.320 align:middle line:90%
It's no good screaming.

00:42:20.320 --> 00:42:24.860 align:middle line:84%
You just have to speak calmly
and not make the other person

00:42:24.860 --> 00:42:28.060 align:middle line:84%
guilty, not shame or
blame the other person.

00:42:28.060 --> 00:42:30.650 align:middle line:90%
Help the other person.

00:42:30.650 --> 00:42:35.320 align:middle line:84%
Both men and women are in a
catastrophic, dissociated,

00:42:35.320 --> 00:42:39.290 align:middle line:84%
horrifically painful situation
in which both are cut off

00:42:39.290 --> 00:42:41.410 align:middle line:90%
from the best of each other.

00:42:41.410 --> 00:42:42.420 align:middle line:90%
Let's get real.

00:42:42.420 --> 00:42:43.490 align:middle line:90%
Let's get together.

00:42:43.490 --> 00:42:45.580 align:middle line:84%
Let's work out ways in
which we can share this.

00:42:45.580 --> 00:42:47.930 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: This takes incredible
maturity and courage.

00:42:47.930 --> 00:42:51.550 align:middle line:84%
And you're looking
on behalf of women.

00:42:51.550 --> 00:42:56.060 align:middle line:84%
What you'll often
see is that that pain

00:42:56.060 --> 00:42:58.017 align:middle line:84%
that's coming up closer
to the surface now,

00:42:58.017 --> 00:43:00.350 align:middle line:84%
that outrage, which is basically
standing up and saying,

00:43:00.350 --> 00:43:00.850 align:middle line:90%
no more.

00:43:00.850 --> 00:43:01.349 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:43:01.349 --> 00:43:03.280 align:middle line:84%
>>HARVEY: And there's a
good thing about that.

00:43:03.280 --> 00:43:05.071 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: There is a
good thing about that.

00:43:05.071 --> 00:43:08.860 align:middle line:84%
But at the same time,
because of an innate need

00:43:08.860 --> 00:43:13.470 align:middle line:84%
for a type of really
almost cellular security,

00:43:13.470 --> 00:43:17.230 align:middle line:84%
which is running throughout
our historical DNA,

00:43:17.230 --> 00:43:20.040 align:middle line:84%
this need for security,
there is a fear of the women

00:43:20.040 --> 00:43:23.600 align:middle line:84%
to speak up and share
that rage because they're

00:43:23.600 --> 00:43:25.170 align:middle line:84%
afraid they'll
lose what they have

00:43:25.170 --> 00:43:27.770 align:middle line:84%
by way of their
secure relationship.

00:43:27.770 --> 00:43:31.407 align:middle line:84%
And so they continue even now,
with it surfacing, stuffing it.

00:43:31.407 --> 00:43:33.615 align:middle line:84%
>>HARVEY: Well I think that
what you're talking about

00:43:33.615 --> 00:43:36.970 align:middle line:84%
is something that Jesus is
very, very brilliant on,

00:43:36.970 --> 00:43:42.290 align:middle line:84%
too, because Jesus shows us
that outrage is essential.

00:43:42.290 --> 00:43:44.650 align:middle line:84%
If you're not outraged,
you're not human.

00:43:44.650 --> 00:43:47.470 align:middle line:84%
But that outrage
is just not enough.

00:43:47.470 --> 00:43:50.120 align:middle line:84%
You have to be able to
transmute that outrage

00:43:50.120 --> 00:43:52.550 align:middle line:90%
into fierce compassion energy.

00:43:52.550 --> 00:43:57.700 align:middle line:84%
So what I would suggest to
women is, and very respectfully,

00:43:57.700 --> 00:44:01.150 align:middle line:84%
is that they come together
and empower each other

00:44:01.150 --> 00:44:02.230 align:middle line:90%
in that outrage.

00:44:02.230 --> 00:44:04.200 align:middle line:90%
Really voice it with each other.

00:44:04.200 --> 00:44:06.070 align:middle line:90%
Get it out.

00:44:06.070 --> 00:44:08.320 align:middle line:84%
And then work with
divine practices

00:44:08.320 --> 00:44:15.530 align:middle line:84%
so that that outrage becomes
that laser calm, clear vision.

00:44:15.530 --> 00:44:19.780 align:middle line:84%
Then men will be deeply
humiliated by the outrage.

00:44:19.780 --> 00:44:22.290 align:middle line:90%
And they will hear the love.

00:44:22.290 --> 00:44:24.560 align:middle line:84%
That doesn't mean that
women have to in any way

00:44:24.560 --> 00:44:27.660 align:middle line:84%
mitigate what they know,
or soften what they say,

00:44:27.660 --> 00:44:31.671 align:middle line:84%
or in any way not get
their deep point across.

00:44:31.671 --> 00:44:33.170 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But dumping
it on your man

00:44:33.170 --> 00:44:34.563 align:middle line:90%
is not working well right now.

00:44:34.563 --> 00:44:35.104 align:middle line:90%
>>HARVEY: No.

00:44:35.104 --> 00:44:36.062 align:middle line:90%
And you can't be heard.

00:44:36.062 --> 00:44:38.760 align:middle line:84%
If I scream at you,
even if I'm screaming

00:44:38.760 --> 00:44:41.540 align:middle line:84%
absolutely true things,
you're going to resist it.

00:44:41.540 --> 00:44:44.130 align:middle line:84%
That's just how human
beings are built.

00:44:44.130 --> 00:44:47.550 align:middle line:84%
I know very wonderful
women who are outraged,

00:44:47.550 --> 00:44:50.350 align:middle line:84%
who do know this
about the patriarchy,

00:44:50.350 --> 00:44:54.100 align:middle line:84%
but who love their men enough
to be able to work on it

00:44:54.100 --> 00:44:57.630 align:middle line:84%
and to be able to say what
they need to say in a way

00:44:57.630 --> 00:44:59.060 align:middle line:90%
that men can hear.

00:44:59.060 --> 00:45:03.980 align:middle line:84%
And there's a very simple rule,
which my women friends tell me,

00:45:03.980 --> 00:45:08.870 align:middle line:84%
which is first tell the guy how
much you really care about him.

00:45:08.870 --> 00:45:11.510 align:middle line:84%
Tell him how much
you appreciate him.

00:45:11.510 --> 00:45:13.800 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Set the scene
softly and gently.

00:45:13.800 --> 00:45:14.300 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:45:14.300 --> 00:45:17.970 align:middle line:84%
>>HARVEY: And then be very
clear, and very lucid,

00:45:17.970 --> 00:45:23.790 align:middle line:84%
and very, very to the point
about what needs to be changed.

00:45:23.790 --> 00:45:26.857 align:middle line:84%
But you'll never get anybody to
change anything, especially not

00:45:26.857 --> 00:45:30.840 align:middle line:84%
a man, if you humiliate him and
make him feel like a killer.

00:45:30.840 --> 00:45:32.490 align:middle line:90%
He'll just say, damn it.

00:45:32.490 --> 00:45:35.450 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to just be the
person that she thinks I am,

00:45:35.450 --> 00:45:37.520 align:middle line:84%
because she's not
giving me the juice.

00:45:37.520 --> 00:45:39.954 align:middle line:84%
She's not giving me what
I need from a woman.

00:45:39.954 --> 00:45:40.870 align:middle line:90%
I need her tenderness.

00:45:40.870 --> 00:45:43.010 align:middle line:90%
And I need her acceptance.

00:45:43.010 --> 00:45:45.230 align:middle line:84%
And then I'll change
anything for her.

00:45:45.230 --> 00:45:48.436 align:middle line:84%
And the same for the-- does
that make any sense to you?

00:45:48.436 --> 00:45:49.310 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:45:49.310 --> 00:45:49.810 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:45:49.810 --> 00:45:51.335 align:middle line:90%
It makes perfect sense.

00:45:51.335 --> 00:45:53.460 align:middle line:84%
>>HARVEY: And the
same for the man.

00:45:53.460 --> 00:45:57.650 align:middle line:84%
Love your woman enough that
when she drives you nuts,

00:45:57.650 --> 00:45:59.560 align:middle line:90%
don't shout at her.

00:45:59.560 --> 00:46:01.790 align:middle line:84%
Don't batter her
emotionally, God

00:46:01.790 --> 00:46:04.290 align:middle line:84%
knows, and certainly
not physically.

00:46:04.290 --> 00:46:05.220 align:middle line:90%
Take it.

00:46:05.220 --> 00:46:07.480 align:middle line:90%
And then work on it.

00:46:07.480 --> 00:46:10.310 align:middle line:84%
And then offer her
your love for her.

00:46:10.310 --> 00:46:12.810 align:middle line:84%
And then say, I would
be-- maybe I'm wrong,

00:46:12.810 --> 00:46:14.820 align:middle line:90%
but this is what I'm feeling.

00:46:14.820 --> 00:46:19.000 align:middle line:84%
Please let me share with
you how, when you do that,

00:46:19.000 --> 00:46:20.110 align:middle line:90%
it makes me feel.

00:46:20.110 --> 00:46:22.440 align:middle line:84%
And I know you don't
want me to feel that.

00:46:22.440 --> 00:46:24.885 align:middle line:84%
So let's find another
way of doing this.

00:46:24.885 --> 00:46:27.090 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And we're
a brave generation.

00:46:27.090 --> 00:46:30.620 align:middle line:84%
This is the bridge generation
that has chosen to break away.

00:46:30.620 --> 00:46:32.370 align:middle line:84%
And also, it's
not-- we've chosen

00:46:32.370 --> 00:46:33.570 align:middle line:90%
to incarnate at this time.

00:46:33.570 --> 00:46:35.730 align:middle line:84%
And the frequencies,
the cosmic frequencies

00:46:35.730 --> 00:46:37.335 align:middle line:84%
are supporting this
transformation.

00:46:37.335 --> 00:46:38.710 align:middle line:84%
>>HARVEY: We're
choosing to marry

00:46:38.710 --> 00:46:40.140 align:middle line:90%
the masculine and the feminine.

00:46:40.140 --> 00:46:42.280 align:middle line:90%
Everyone is on that journey.

00:46:42.280 --> 00:46:45.000 align:middle line:84%
That Jesus is coming
back to us, the Jesus

00:46:45.000 --> 00:46:47.360 align:middle line:84%
of the sacred
marriage, to help us

00:46:47.360 --> 00:46:50.130 align:middle line:84%
fuse the masculine and feminine,
heaven and Earth, matter

00:46:50.130 --> 00:46:50.990 align:middle line:90%
and spirit.

00:46:50.990 --> 00:46:52.910 align:middle line:84%
And get on with the
business of transforming

00:46:52.910 --> 00:46:54.757 align:middle line:84%
the planet before
we all explode.

00:46:54.757 --> 00:46:55.340 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:46:55.340 --> 00:46:58.840 align:middle line:84%
Now we're going to go on from
there to one of the bridges.

00:46:58.840 --> 00:47:02.340 align:middle line:84%
And that can be the work
of Rumi and the concepts

00:47:02.340 --> 00:47:05.340 align:middle line:84%
that Rumi was trying
to-- well the divinity

00:47:05.340 --> 00:47:07.290 align:middle line:84%
that he was trying to
relate to humanity.

00:47:07.290 --> 00:47:09.325 align:middle line:84%
And you've been
studying Rumi for, what?

00:47:09.325 --> 00:47:09.940 align:middle line:90%
40 years.

00:47:09.940 --> 00:47:10.630 align:middle line:90%
This is your passion.

00:47:10.630 --> 00:47:11.921 align:middle line:90%
>>HARVEY: Although I'm only 42.

00:47:11.921 --> 00:47:13.014 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:47:13.014 --> 00:47:14.430 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Gosh,
you started early.

00:47:14.430 --> 00:47:16.719 align:middle line:84%
But then you did start reading
very young, I've heard.

00:47:16.719 --> 00:47:17.260 align:middle line:90%
>>HARVEY: No.

00:47:17.260 --> 00:47:17.764 align:middle line:90%
I'm 60.

00:47:17.764 --> 00:47:18.520 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:47:18.520 --> 00:47:21.710 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So with
Rumi, what is the piece

00:47:21.710 --> 00:47:25.960 align:middle line:84%
of Rumi in terms of the divinity
and purity of love from-- just

00:47:25.960 --> 00:47:28.720 align:middle line:84%
from within between ourselves
and the divine-- not even

00:47:28.720 --> 00:47:30.830 align:middle line:84%
expressing yet with
another human being--

00:47:30.830 --> 00:47:34.960 align:middle line:84%
that you cherish so much
and can share with us?

00:47:34.960 --> 00:47:38.583 align:middle line:84%
And the Christ concepts
that he also embraced.

00:47:38.583 --> 00:47:39.166 align:middle line:90%
>>HARVEY: Yes.

00:47:39.166 --> 00:47:40.457 align:middle line:90%
It all goes together, actually.

00:47:40.457 --> 00:47:42.630 align:middle line:84%
This is such a
momentous discovery

00:47:42.630 --> 00:47:45.190 align:middle line:84%
that's really been made
in the last 30 years.

00:47:45.190 --> 00:47:49.460 align:middle line:90%
And it goes like this.

00:47:49.460 --> 00:47:53.090 align:middle line:84%
Rumi was, of course,
Islamic and Muslim.

00:47:53.090 --> 00:47:55.030 align:middle line:84%
But many people
don't know that Jesus

00:47:55.030 --> 00:47:57.190 align:middle line:84%
plays an immense
role in the Quran.

00:47:57.190 --> 00:48:00.950 align:middle line:84%
He is celebrated as a
great, great prophet.

00:48:00.950 --> 00:48:04.080 align:middle line:84%
And also, he's given the role
of bringing in the rule of God

00:48:04.080 --> 00:48:04.957 align:middle line:90%
at the end of time.

00:48:04.957 --> 00:48:06.665 align:middle line:84%
It isn't prophet
Muhammad who comes back.

00:48:06.665 --> 00:48:08.000 align:middle line:90%
It's Jesus.

00:48:08.000 --> 00:48:10.570 align:middle line:84%
Also, in the Sufi
mystical tradition,

00:48:10.570 --> 00:48:13.460 align:middle line:84%
the Islamic mystical
tradition, Jesus

00:48:13.460 --> 00:48:18.110 align:middle line:84%
appears to the mystic at
a time when that mystic

00:48:18.110 --> 00:48:20.410 align:middle line:84%
has achieved a level
of divine love.

